黄晓明、林志玲捐的扶贫基金会赠170万口罩？供货商称：不做口罩，从未卖口罩给基金会。
Huang Xiaoming, Lin Zhiling donated 1.7 million masks to the foundation. The supplier said: Do not make masks, never sell them to the foundation.
