出品|网易清流工作室作者|刘亚丹 主编|赵妍爆料邮箱：stoolpigeon@service.netease.com没有购销N95资质的口罩供应商，出现在一家基金会供货合同中。
Running Netease & # 44; & # 45; & # 45; & # 44; & # 44; & # 44; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 44; & # 44; & # 44; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
不是口罩生产商，曾因医疗器械违规被处罚，口罩采购价格还被指高于市场价格。
Mask makers, who have been punished for malpractice in medical devices, have been accused of buying masks at a price higher than the market price.
看似不合理背后，这家“口罩供应商”回复清流工作室称：“我们没有卖口罩给基金会，我们不做口罩。
"We don't sell masks to the foundation, and we don't make masks," the mask supplier responded to Cleaning Studio.
”1月30日，湖北省红十字会公布的一张银行卡信息引起了各方关注，该银行付款回单中，将收款人开户行“中国银行北京幸福广场支行”中的“支”行写为“之”行。
On January 30, attention was drawn to information on a bank card issued by the Red Cross Society of Hubei Province, which in its payment return lists the "branch" line in the bank's "Bank of China's happiness square branch in Beijing" as the "branch."
一时间，被指为假P图银行卡转账信息。
For a while, was accused of being a fake P-chart bank card transfer information.
此外，该电子回单中公示的金额，与收款方中华思源工程扶贫基金会对外公示的金额相差20万。
In addition, the amount disclosed in the electronic return differed by 200,000 from the amount disclosed to the public by the recipient, the China National Resources Engineering Poverty Alleviation Foundation.
与此同时，该银行卡收款方中华思源工程扶贫基金会（以下简称:”思源基金会”)也引起大众关注。
At the same time, the bank card recipient, the Chinese Siyuan Project Poverty Alleviation Foundation (hereinafter: "Siyuan Foundation") also attracted public attention.
网易清流工作室注意到，这家基金会五年累积捐赠收入比公益支出多1.83亿元，除了公益支出，该基金会还是一家风险投资公司的股东。
The Netease Clearing Studio noted that the foundation's five-year cumulative donation income exceeded its public-interest spending by 183 million yuan, and that it was a shareholder in a venture-capital firm, in addition to public-interest spending.
1月26日，思源基金会官微公告称，第一期项目善款共计435万元物资于近日发出，并且在附件中公布了拟采购口罩的合同，包括20万个N95口罩、50万个一次性外科口罩和100万个一次性医用口罩，合计170万个口罩。
On January 26, the Siyuan Foundation announced in a notice that the first phase of the project, worth 4.35 million yuan in donations, had recently issued a contract for the purchase of masks, including 200,000 N95 masks, 500,000 disposable surgical masks and 1 million disposable medical masks, making a total of 1.7 million masks.
但是清流工作室联系到思源基金会披露的口罩供应商——深圳南方联合健康产业有限公司，该公司回复称：“我们没有卖口罩给基金会，我们不做口罩。
"We don't sell masks to the foundation, and we don't make masks," the company replied, referring to Siyuan's disclosure of mask suppliers, Shenzhen Southern United Health Industry Co., Ltd.
”值得注意的是，思源基金会公开的的口罩采购合同中，只有思源基金会一方的盖章，无深圳南方联合健康产业有限公司的盖章和签字。
Notably, the Siyuan Foundation's public contract for the purchase of face masks contains only the seal of the Siyuan Foundation and no seal or signature of the Shenzhen Southern United Health Industry Co. Ltd.
此外，思源基金会公开合同中供应商的地址——深圳市罗湖区南湖街道嘉宾路太平洋商贸大厦B座22L单元，与深圳南方联合健康产业有限公司公开的工商注册地址也完全吻合。
In addition, the address of the supplier in the open contract of Siyuan Foundation - Unit 22L, Block B, Pacific Business Building, Nanhu Street, South Lake District, Shenzhen, is also in good agreement with the public business registration address of Shenzhen Southern Joint Health Industry Co. Ltd.
清流工作室随后再次联系到深圳南方联合健康产业有限公司法人代表及100%股权控制人陈晓东，陈晓东回复称：“我们做医疗设备”，不卖口罩，更不卖N95口罩。
"We make medical equipment," Chen answered, referring to the company's legal representative and 100% stake controller Chen Xiaodong. "We don't sell masks, let alone N95 masks."
清流工作室多次联系思源基金会核查上述信息，该基金会工作人员称不清楚上述情况，推荐联系基金会宣传部门。
The Clearing Stream Studios contacted the Siyuan Foundation several times to verify the above information, and the staff of the Foundation stated that they were unaware of the situation and recommended contacting the Foundation's communications department.
截止发稿前，该基金会宣传部门电话，一直处于占线状态。
Before the deadline, the foundation's propaganda department phone, has been in a busy state.
思源基金会26日发布的官方微博称，“正在与医疗物资供货方签署购买协议”，因供货方在异地，待双方合同盖章完后进一步公示。
"We are in the process of signing a purchase agreement with the suppliers of medical materials," said the official Weibo, released on the 26th by the Siyuan Foundation.
但是在物资紧急的疫情期，截止到1月30日晚，该基金会未做该合同的进一步公示。
But during the emergency period, as of the night of January 30, the foundation did not give further publicity to the contract.
（图片来自中华思源工程扶贫基金会官方微博）蹊跷的口罩捐赠合作方武汉新型肺炎病毒疫情中，中华思源工程扶贫基金会对外接收了众多明星的捐款。
(Photo taken from the official microblog of the China Siyuan Project Poverty Alleviation Foundation) The China Siyuan Project Poverty Alleviation Foundation has received donations from a number of celebrities during the new pneumonia virus outbreak in Wuhan.
公开资料显示，截止1月28日上午，中华思源工程扶贫基金会公布了61位明星的捐款名单，可见名单中主要有黄晓明、杨颖、吴京、谢楠、管虎、梁静、张大大、井柏然等61人，截至1月27日23时59分演艺界爱心明星捐款共计1326.2万。
As of the morning of January 28, the CSSW Foundation for Poverty Alleviation announced a list of 61 celebrity donations, including 61 people, including Huang Xiaoming, Yang Ying, Wu Jing, Shanan, Guanghu, Liang Jing, Zhang Da, and Jing Pak Ran.
1月26日，思源基金会官微公告称，第一期项目善款共计435万元物资于近日发出，并且在附件中公布了拟采购口罩的合同，包括20万个N95口罩、50万个一次性外科口罩和100万个一次性医用口罩。
A total of 4.35 million yuan was donated recently for the first phase of the project, which includes 200,000 N95 masks, 500,000 disposable surgical masks and 1 million disposable medical masks, an official notice said on January 26.
但是公开信息显示，思源基金会的口罩供货商——深圳南方联合健康产业有限公司没有购销N95口罩的资质，也不是口罩直接生产商，而是医疗器械的销售方。
But according to public information, Siyuan's mask supplier, Shenzhen Southern United Health Industry Co. Ltd. is not qualified to sell N95 masks, nor is it a direct manufacturer of masks, but a seller of medical devices.
这家公司还曾经因为医疗器械违法，2018年被深圳罗湖食品药品监督管理局处罚。
The company was also fined in 2018 by the Shenzhen Luohu Food and Drug Administration for illegal medical devices.
市场关于深圳南方联合健康产业有限公司的新闻，也多是医院大型医疗器械的合作中标方。
Market information about Shenzhen Southern United Health Industry Co. Ltd. is also the hospital large-scale medical equipment cooperation winning party.
按照市场供销规律，口罩的生产商才更可能提供最低的价格。
Mask makers are more likely to offer the lowest price according to market rules.
天眼查显示，深圳南方联合健康产业有限公司的行业属性属于软件和信息服务业，主经营范围是医疗器械的销售和健康产业投资，没有口罩的生产资质。
The industry attributes of Shenzhen Southern United Health Industry Co. Ltd. belong to the software and information service industry. Its main business scope is the sale of medical devices and investment in health industry.
此外，该公司的经营范围是一类医疗器械的购销，但是N95口罩属于“二类依赖器械”，也就是说该公司并没有购销N95口罩的资质。
In addition, the company is engaged in the purchase and sale of medical devices, but N95 masks are "Category Two Dependent Appliances," meaning that the company is not qualified to buy and sell N95 masks.
思源基金会对外称，合同中的单价，为多方联系询价比价后选定，选择物资符合疫区使用标准。
Siyuan Foundation external said that the unit price in the contract, for the multi-contact inquiry after the selection of materials meet the criteria for use of epidemic areas.
根据基金会公开的合同显示，当次购买的外科口罩单价为1.1元。
The cost of the surgical mask purchased was 1.1 yuan, according to the foundation's public contract.
一位医疗器械销售行业人士告诉清流工作室，“这个价格相对目前市场偏高，但是也在正常范围内。
"The price is high relative to the current market, but within normal limits," a medical device sales person told Clear Stream Studio.
”捐赠收入比公益支出多1.83亿元 基金会被多次起诉网易清流工作室注意到，思源基金会五年累积捐赠收入比公益支出多1.83亿元。
Donations exceeded public-interest spending by 183 million yuan The foundation has been sued several times by Netease Studio, noting that the five-year cumulative donation revenue of the Cisco Foundation exceeded public utility spending by 183 million yuan.
多余的钱流向何处？清流工作室查到，思源基金会是中国风险投资公司的股东，2015年曾出资1000万购入中国风险投资公司5%股份。
Where does the extra money go? The Clearing Stream Studios found that the Siyuan Foundation, a shareholder in Chinese venture capital firms, paid $10m for a 5 per cent stake in a Chinese venture-capital firm in 2015.
值得注意的是，同年，中国风险投资公司曾经因为提供了不真实的统计资料，被北京市朝阳区统计局处罚。
Notably, in the same year, Chinese venture capital firms were penalized by the Beijing Chaoyang District Bureau of Statistics for providing untrue statistics.
此外，该基金会还因为曾经的一项公益惠民项目被多位自然人起诉。
In addition, the Foundation has been sued by a number of natural persons for a former pro bono project.
2014年4月，四川惜净实业有限公司法定代表人吴自刚与中央民建下属中华思源工程扶贫基金会取得联系，并于同年6月签订合作协议，成立了"中华思源工程扶贫基金会净爱公益基金"（以下简称"净爱基金"），吴自刚任“思源净爱基金”的管委会主任。
In April 2014, Wu Zhigang, legal representative of Sichuan Xijing Industrial Co., Ltd., contacted the China Resources Engineering Poverty Alleviation Foundation under the Central People's Government and signed a cooperation agreement in June of the same year.
2014年8月12日四川民建主办惠民洗衣启动，惠民洗衣在四川省开展工作为60岁以上老人免费洗衣，15岁以下儿童免费洗衣，为残疾人士，伤残军人免费洗衣，免费为享受政策内的人员发放洗衣粉，肥皂，衣物等物品。
On August 12, 2014, Huimin Laundry was set up in Sichuan Province to provide free laundry for people over 60, laundry for children under the age of 15, laundry for the disabled and the disabled, and laundry powder, soap and clothing for those enjoying the policy.
“净爱公益基金”对外宣称，从事洗涤联盟的各地服务站站长，对特定贫困人群的免费洗衣服务，基金管委会按扶助补贴标准提供洗衣服务补贴。
"Net Love public welfare fund" announced that the washing union in the local service stations, for certain poor people free laundry services, the fund management committee at the rate of subsidies to provide laundry services.
但是吴自刚后迫于债务压力，在未获正式授权的情况下，冒用"净爱基金"管委会资质，伪造公章和授权文件，篡改与中华思源工程扶贫基金会的协议内容，虚构可获得"净爱基金"拨款的"惠民洗衣"公益项目擅自招募加盟商，并向加盟的代理商和服务站收取高额"保证金"共计人民币1480余万元，致使惠民洗衣各地投资人，各服务站损失惨重。
But under pressure of debt, Wu used Rmb14.8 million without formal authorization to use & quot; RCCs qualification, forged official seals and authorization documents, falsified agreements with Sinopec & amp; Poor's Foundation; created & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot; & quot
截止到2019年10月，网络上还有因该项政策亏损的投资人投诉信息。
As of October 2019, there was also information on complaints from investors who had lost money on the policy.
